{# Reusable metric summary header.

   Used above the chart tile on the dashboard AND on each metric
   detail page. Same pattern for every metric: a name + a one-line
   headline.

   Required context:
     summary.title    — short metric name, e.g. "Cycle time"
     summary.headline — one-line statement, e.g.
                         "43 items completed · P50 0.1d · P85 1.4d · P95 7.8d"
#}
<div class="metric-summary">
  {# H3 (subsection), not H2 (eyebrow). H2 in the Knox design
     system is UPPERCASE — wrong for a metric name like "Cycle
     time". H2 is reserved here for in-page section headings like
     "How to read this" / "Caveats" on detail pages. #}
  <h3 class="metric-summary-title">{{ summary.title }}</h3>
  <p class="metric-summary-headline">{{ summary.headline }}</p>
</div>
